{"tid":1725034,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"全體和理非心聲: 就算有錯, 都我哋嘅錯!","createTime":"2019-11-15T15:36:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T06:54:21.000Z","uid":252069,"like":62,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"2c76f0a790432132023ef4a0a42fd63f53871db2","tid":1725034,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:36:28.000Z","msg":"我哋和理非明明同是爭取五大訴求<br />\n但係前線手足打生打死<br />\n我哋就將<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">抗爭外判</span></span></strong>, 淨係識匿喺屋企做鍵盤戰士, 最多落街屌黑警<br />\n有不反嘅遊行比黑警嚇兩嚇就<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">縮沙</span></span></strong><br />\n連罷工呢d咁無危險性嘅事我哋都做到<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">唔湯唔水</span></strong></span><br />\n呢兩日好似有令黑警收一收手完全係手足<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">搵命博</span></span></strong>返來<br />\n<br />\n講返今日七十歲過身嗰位伯伯, 係我哋嘅和理非嘅錯<br />\n雖然係人定鬼打定TK都未知, 但係有人死一定無人想<br />\n呢個係悲劇, 我好傷心<br />\n然而出人命我唔會怪前線手足<br />\n因為就算係藍絲死都係我哋和理非出唔夠力, 導致<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">藍更藍黃更黃都係因為我</span></strong></span><br />\n仲滿口仁義道德話死咗人係前線太過份, 同為和理非我睇到覺得自己<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好醜</span></span></strong><br />\n我自問無資格屌手足, 我自問<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">廢到無得再廢</span></span></strong>, 但係我仲想幫手<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">點幫手?</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n手足做得唔完美要改善一定有, 對某d人造成損害都有一定<br />\n然而任何人要怪罪搵人負責, 入我哋數!<br />\n要賠錢就由我哋出, 衰d講就算要坐監就由我哋去坐!<br />\n明明我哋都佔一樣大嘅責任, 我哋仲行得走得, 有手足<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">斷手斷腳失明冇命</span></strong></span><br />\n仲屌手足我就唔敢再講自己有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">廉恥!</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n成日話好彩贏咗就話煲底除裝相見<br />\n我話你知就算加埋你好彩到冇一個前線手足要坐監<br />\n都只係得少部份前線手足可以無穿無爛仲<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">行得走得</span></strong></span>出來同你見<br />\n有少少差池我真係無面目見你哋<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">唔割</span></span></strong>唔係口號, 係覺得自己唔係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">苟且偷生</span></strong></span>嘅信念!<br />\n<br />\n你哋自己睇<br />\n我成年後直到今年六月前加埋無喊過三次<br />\n但呢個係唯一一樣野令我諗親都眼紅鼻酸<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i2Nw61z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi2Nw61z.jpg&h=7f6c14fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CzTbtTFM7Zw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCzTbtTFM7Zw&d=1ryX%2BwltUSTIgmnFzyWg%2BG5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=ca856cec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CzTbtTFM7Zw</a>"},{"pid":"0af28a470bed0b6d83251c9593e3f053beda9d8f","tid":1725034,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:37:39.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},{"pid":"d74b32afc83acddeda9ab39e3d523686d50e0c8e","tid":1725034,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:38:01.000Z","msg":"自推 2/10"},{"pid":"f1ad04070829b84da469020b0d9046e44ad725f8","tid":1725034,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:43:26.000Z","msg":"自推 3/10"},{"pid":"717146d6555a88280a10aee282a401e8bd17a709","tid":1725034,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:43:38.000Z","msg":"自推 4/10"},{"pid":"8efac529d4bfe4eb47010f79aac306fd51fae3c2","tid":1725034,"uid":273620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:43:40.000Z","msg":"行動post冇人推!!! 11.23用比三罷更強既和理非武器去打擊春袋中既春袋！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1725006\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1725006</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fc04d44da578e06bdac3eb3ff94282bf49019445","tid":1725034,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:44:24.000Z","msg":"自推 5/10"},{"pid":"187fe46cc82da19b630a0a510bfb1beb71a284d2","tid":1725034,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:45:42.000Z","msg":"自推 6/10"},{"pid":"7e52d1a0ab9dd72a7728f90f64a038ef0acac918","tid":1725034,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:46:06.000Z","msg":"自推 7/10"},{"pid":"c5e71d732024317465afbc464fe67dfb0e5d2a1d","tid":1725034,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:46:28.000Z","msg":"自推 8/10"},{"pid":"016ddaeb82aff0598dbf68e2508db17eb97f1387","tid":1725034,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:47:05.000Z","msg":"自推 9/10"},{"pid":"5cb879ffd75f1256aac865b7e81f172f8839889c","tid":1725034,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:47:19.000Z","msg":"自推 10/10"},{"pid":"156cfe2c2113f3f48fd7afc3d461ffa1f96e90f2","tid":1725034,"uid":108757,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:47:55.000Z","msg":"唔洗矮化自己，慢慢進化就得，每個崗位都要人做，喺自己崗位做足一百分就夠"},{"pid":"d8764359b7cb5fc23d4234028d1dc2290ee7054d","tid":1725034,"uid":243588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:50:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"032f1b2565489f1f13de315d816f018dd048b940","tid":1725034,"uid":115988,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:08:28.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n解散警隊 刻不容緩<br />\n揸緊信念 煲底相見<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eda2c2716f427d8dc44e09bcffe90d3c4d070cc1","tid":1725034,"uid":204093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:09:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd57aa84e43c6d1260e6dae518b9b9d9a31723be","tid":1725034,"uid":178887,"like":0,"dis